%% Diagram: End-to-end request sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Br as Browser
    participant LB as Load Balancer
    participant API as Ingestion API<br/>(WebFlux)
    participant K as Kafka<br/>(csp-violations)
    participant Co as Consumer
    participant R as Valkey<br/>(dedup)
    participant S as Snowflake

    Br->>LB: POST /csp/report
    LB->>API: forward
    API->>API: parse + validate JSON
    API-->>K: produce (acks=1)
    API-->>Br: 204 No Content
    Note over API,Br: Response is sent before<br/>Kafka ack returns.
    Co->>K: poll batch
    Co->>Co: normalize + hash
    Co->>R: SET hash NX EX 600
    alt new violation
        R-->>Co: OK
        Co->>S: micro-batch insert
    else duplicate
        R-->>Co: nil
        Co->>Co: drop record
    end
    Co->>K: commit offset
